    INNER JOIN [Sizes] AS [x.Size0] ON [x0].[SizeId] = [x.Size0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [x.Product0] ON [x0].[ProductId] = [x.Product0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [x.Product.ProductCategory0] ON [x.Product0].[CategoryId] = [x.Product.ProductCategory0].[Id]
    WHERE [x0].[ProductId] = @__productId_0
) AS [t] ON [x.Product.ProductCategory.Products].[CategoryId] = [t].[Id0]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)

VALUES (@p2, @p3, @p4, 0),
(@p5, @p6, @p7, 1),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, 2)) AS i ([Caption], [Path], [ProductId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Caption], [Path], [ProductId])
VALUES (i.[Caption], i.[Path], i.[ProductId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted2;

    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [x.Product].[Name], [x.Product].[CategoryId], [x.Product].[Image], [x.Product].[Price], [x.Product].[PromotionPrice], [x.Product].[OriginalPrice], [x.Product].[Description], [x.Product].[Content], [x.Product].[HomeFlag], [x.Product].[HotFlag], [x.Product].[ViewCount], [x.Product].[Tags], [x.Product].[Unit], CASE
    WHEN [x.Product].[CategoryId] IS NOT NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [x.Product.ProductCategory].[Id], [x.Product.ProductCategory].[Name] AS [Name0], [x.Product.ProductCategory].[Description] AS [Description0], [x.Product.ProductCategory].[ParentId], [x.Product.ProductCategory].[HomeOrder], [x.Product.ProductCategory].[Image] AS [Image0], [x.Product.ProductCategory].[HomeFlag] AS [HomeFlag0], [x.Product.ProductCategory].[DateCreated], [x.Product.ProductCategory].[DateModified], [x.Product.ProductCategory].[SortOrder], [x.Product.ProductCategory].[Status], [x.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoPageTitle], [x.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoAlias], [x.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoKeywords], [x.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoDescription], [x.Product].[SeoPageTitle] AS [SeoPageTitle0], [x.Product].[SeoAlias] AS [SeoAlias0], [x.Product].[SeoKeywords] AS [SeoKeywords0], [x.Product].[SeoDescription] AS [SeoDescription0], [x.Product].[DateCreated] AS [DateCreated0], [x.Product].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [x.Product].[Status] AS [Status0], CASE
    WHEN [x].[SizeId] IS NOT NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [x.Size].[Name] AS [Name1], CASE
    WHEN [x].[ColorId] IS NOT NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [x.Color].[Name] AS [Name2], [x.Color].[Code]
FROM [ProductQuantities] AS [x]
INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [x.Color] ON [x].[ColorId] = [x.Color].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Sizes] AS [x.Size] ON [x].[SizeId] = [x.Size].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [x.Product] ON [x].[ProductId] = [x.Product].[Id]
